{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/row-number-와-partition을-이용한-최빈값-뽑기","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"query-row_number-partition\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#query-row_number-partition\" aria-label=\"query row_number partition permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>query? row_number? partition?</h1>\n<h1 id=\"쿼리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BF%BC%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"쿼리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>쿼리</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"query\"><pre class=\"language-query\"><code class=\"language-query\">select * from (                                             \n    select name, row_number() over (partition by userid order by cnt desc) rownum from (    # 2. user별로 partition을 나누어\n        select count(*) cnt, userid, ip from loginlog                                       # 1. user와 ip로 그루핑 후\n        group by userid, ip\n    ) original\n) where rownum=1;                                                                           # 3. 최빈cnt(내림차순 기준 첫번째 rownum)값을 뽑아낸다.</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"작업내용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"작업내용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>작업내용</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">$ wget tomcat\n$ tar -xvf tomcat\n# 설정파일 옮기기\n- tomcat/conf/*.*\n- tomcat/conf/ssl/\n\n# 필요 폴더 생성\n- mkdir tomcat/webapps/dis\ncp -r old/webapps/dis/ new/webapps/\n\n\n# 링크 수정\nln -Tfs [path] [name]   =&gt;  ln -Tfs /home/dis/tomcat/apache-tomcat-9.0.35/ latest\n#</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>6.7을 마지막으로 </li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"vcenter-server-appliance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vcenter-server-appliance\" aria-label=\"vcenter server appliance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vCenter Server Appliance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>리눅스 위에서 돌아감</li>\n<li>-</li>\n</ul>\n<p>전자는 애플리케이션 셋이고 후자는 OS+애플리케이션 셋이라는 차이점이 있으며, </p>\n<ul>\n<l